# Project Overview

This is an animated React demo application called "Hello World React App" that showcases advanced CSS animations and interactive text transitions.

## Key Files
- [App.js](mdc:src/App.js) - Main React component with toggle functionality
- [App.css](mdc:src/App.css) - Complex CSS animations and styling system
- [index.js](mdc:src/index.js) - React root rendering with StrictMode
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [index.html](mdc:public/index.html) - HTML template

## Project Purpose
Demonstrates modern React development with sophisticated visual effects including:
- Text toggle between "Hello World" and "Bye World"
- Multi-layered CSS animations (spinning, sliding, color shifting)
- Gradient backgrounds and animated button interactions
- GitHub Actions integration with Cursor CLI for automated code review

